snippet.title: Two Leaves and a bud - Tea Garden Simulator
snippet.description:
Two leaves and a bud is a tea farm and factory management game. Produce a variety of tea. Craft your own processing technique, expand and manage your Tea Estate. You'll also have to deal with factors such as pests, weather, and labor management, which can either make or break your business.

Coming soon on Steam, Play demo, and wishlist us.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1401340/T
